      <li>Avoid applying for withdrawal on several accounts under your management in a single day as it will be automatically detected and all the withdrawals will be declined whether or not they bear different account names. You are advised to apply on separate days. </li>
      <li>If after 48 hours you don't get your requested fund, kindly allow extra 24 hours before submitting a complaint which may be caused by Bank Reversals most of the times or incorrect bank account details.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>To submit a withdrawal complaint after 72 hours, kindly whatsapp any of the Admins on 07030498562, 07039150972, 07037656329</p>
  <p>Withdrawal Complaint will only be attended to after 72 hours from time of request.</p>
  <p><b>Thanks for your maximum cooperation.</b></p>
                      </ul>
  
